{"word":"G2127 - εὐλογέω - eulogéō - yoo-log-eh'-o - Bless","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εὐλογέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">eulogéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">yoo-log-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Bless</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - ஆசீர்வதி, ஸ்தோத்திரி, துதி"},{"paragraph":"to bless one, to praise, celebrate with praises"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G2095 - εὖ - eû - yoo/2095\">G2095</a> and <a href=\"#/G3056 - λόγος - lógos - log'-os/3056\">G3056</a>; to <i>speak well of</i>, that is, (religiously) to <i>bless</i> (<i>thank</i> or <i>invoke a benediction upon</i>, <i>prosper</i>): - bless, praise.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1757/1757\">G1757</a>, <a href=\"#/G2127/2127\">G2127</a>, <a href=\"#/G2128/2128\">G2128</a>, <a href=\"#/G2129/2129\">G2129</a>"}]}